item.title: How to change the ip for deltascape client?
item.dc:creator: @kedonot1 kedonot1
item.description:
@kedonot1 wrote:

How to change the ip?
Go into Client.java

Go to edit at the top
click Search for
Type 127
Then something like 127.0.0.0
should come up.
Change that to ur ip.
Compile.

item.title: How to change the ip for deltascape client?
item.dc:creator: @xx_qwertyuiop_xx xx qwertyuiop xx
item.description:
@xx_qwertyuiop_xx wrote:

Well, since Runescape clients are quite large, it is not likely that a decompiler will generate the source code without errors.
So you’d probably want to go with a bytecode editor.

I don’t know anything about bytecode editors to be honest, but if you want to download one and play around with it I recommend JBE.
